Daiwa SB Investments Ltd. (DSBI) is an active investment manager specialising in Japanese and Asia ex-Japan equity products.


Our business is global with offices in Tokyo, London, New York, Hong Kong, Singapore and Shanghai. We manage assets on behalf of financial institutions, pension funds, government agencies and retail investors.



















