Daiwa SB Investments Ltd. (DSBI) is an active investment manager specialising in Japanese and Asian equity products.


DSBI began managing active Japan equity mandates in 1973.
Since then, we have developed a reputation with both domestic and overseas clients for the quality of our products and services.
The Japanese equity part of our business represents almost 40% of our assets under management, which is evidence that Japanese equity is our core business.
We are one of the oldest and largest domestic institutional investment managers in Japan.
In addition, we have been managing Asia ex-Japan equity strategies since 1979.
Investment philosophy and style
DSBI’s overall investment philosophy is to “achieve stable excess returns through active management” over the medium-to-long-term, and by taking advantage of market inefficiencies.



















